These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Movie-Genre: satire, time-travel, action, crime
House: modern, cottage, cape-cod, townhouse
1. Movie-Genre:satire is on the right of House:cape-cod##1
2. House:townhouse is on the far left##1
3. House:cape-cod is between House:cottage and Movie-Genre:time-travel##2
4. Movie-Genre:crime is on the far left##1
5. Movie-Genre:action is between Movie-Genre:time-travel and Movie-Genre:satire##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | crime         | time-travel   | action | satire       |
| House      | townhouse | modern | cape-cod   | cottage |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
Flower: rose, marigold, bellflower, iris
Pet: mouse, bird, hamster, rat
1. Pet:rat is between Flower:bellflower and Pet:bird##2
2. Flower:iris is on the far right##1
3. Pet:hamster is on the right of Pet:mouse##1
4. Flower:rose is on the left of Pet:mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Flower         | marigold | rose | bellflower | iris |
| Pet   | bird    | rat   | mouse | hamster       |

